content: I am sorry I am sorry Does it matter? No, I already ruined the party I am sorry Again? All in vain I am sorry You talking to me? No to me, so I don’t shoot me with another arrow I am sorry Why? For letting the fear speak for me I am sorry Now what? I do not know I cannot think All I know is that I am terrified And I want to hide
